alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root first.

- **Specs live in `docs/specs/*.md`** — read the relevant spec before implementing.
- Three tiers, do not cross them: Tier-1 intake = `docs/specs/`; Tier-2 planning =
  `_bmad-output/projects/<slug>/planning-artifacts/`; Tier-3 execution output =
  `_bmad-output/projects/<slug>/implementation-artifacts/` (gitignored/local-only).
- Never put an intake spec into a Tier-3 output dir. Write your own working output under `.cursor/`.
